         GO TO AA15
     END-IF
     IF MOUSE-Y = 24
         IF MOUSE-X = 5
      MOVE 5  TO KEY-CODE-1
      GO TO AA10
         ELSE
         IF MOUSE-X = 10
      MOVE 6  TO KEY-CODE-1
      GO TO AA10
         ELSE
         IF MOUSE-X > 36 AND < 44
      MOVE 0  TO KEY-CODE-1
      GO TO AA10
         ELSE
         IF MOUSE-X > 54 AND < 60
      MOVE 0  TO KEY-CODE-1
      MOVE 1  TO KEY-TYPE
      GO TO AA10
         END-IF
     END-IF
   WHEN ENTER-KEY  GO TO AA15
   WHEN OTHER  CALL X"E5"
        END-EVALUATE
        GO TO AA05
    ELSE
    IF USER-FUNC
        EVALUATE KEY-CODE-1
   WHEN ESC-KEY
       MOVE "0"  TO WS-OPTION
       GO TO AA18
